WILL YOU PLEASE
HOLD IT, FOLKS?

334
00:23:22,609 --> 00:23:24,193
I'D LIKE
TO TAKE
YOUR PICTURE.

335
00:23:24,277 --> 00:23:26,404
GOODNESS. TRY TO MAKE
