336
00:23:26,488 --> 00:23:27,947
OUR PICTURE'S
GONNA BE IN
THE PAPER.

337
00:23:28,031 --> 00:23:29,031
THE COMB!

338
00:23:29,116 --> 00:23:30,157
OH, YEAH!

339
